                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 033.1100 K77/63.]</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tegucigalpa</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-02-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 27, 1912</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>This Government needs to know at once whether the Secretary will come to
                    Tegucigalpa or only to Amapala, in order to make the plans for his
                    reception.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">White.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
